Even with my female friends,
it's hard to talk about that stuff.

00:07:32.985 --> 00:07:34.287
Do you understand that?

00:07:34.387 --> 00:07:36.122
Well, I guess.

00:07:40.193 --> 00:07:42.462
You're the very one
who hides everything about yourself.

00:07:45.031 --> 00:07:46.032
What?

00:07:46.332 --> 00:07:50.002
